<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-72-0148 </DOCNO><TEXT>Following a description of the stresses on fire-resistant lining of communalrefuse incineration plants, modern lining concepts are introduced. Inlaboratory investigations the oxidation resistance of various types ofSiC stone offered in the market have been analysed and the differentbehaviour of oxide- and nitride-related qualities are discussed. In conclusionviews are expressed on SiC stud pipe materials.</TEXT></DOC>